                            <h2>Sumo Rules</h2>
                            <ol>
                                <li>Bouts for competitor six years and under will be 1 minute long Note: A bout is equal to 1 point.)</li>
                                <li>Bouts for competitors above six years will be 1 and half minutes long (Note: A bout is equal to 1 point.)</li>
                                <li>Competitor/s who is ahead after best of three (3) scoring bouts or who ever is ahead when time permits, will be declared the winner</li>
                                <li>Where weight categories are required, ensure your correct weight is recorded within the closet kilo rounded up on your entry form.<br>
                                E.g. If you are 45.6kg recorded your weight on your form as 46kg not 45.6kg, as 46kg will be to the closet kilo.</li>
                                <li>You may also on the day of the tournament be requiring to be weighed by the officials, before you can compete.</li>
