                            No charging at your opponent at any time.
                            No Lifting of the leg of any type to an opponent.
                            No Sweeping of the legs allowed.</p>
                            <h2>Equipment Required</h2>
                            <p>Headgear, Mouth guard and Full Martial Arts Uniform must be worn Karate Kung fu or Taekwondo Gi with long sleeves (No Exceptions).</p>
